    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated that Ubayy bin Kab said:\nI taught a man the Quran, and he gave me a bow. I mentioned that to the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) and he said: If you accept it you will be accepting a bow of fire. So I returned it.',
