    hadithEnglish:
      'It was narrated that Ibn Abbas said:\nWhen the Prophet (ﷺ) came to Al-Madinah, they were the worst people in weights and measures. Then Allah, Glorious is He revealed: Woe to the Mutaffifun (those who give less in measure and weight), and they were fair in weights and measures after that.',
