      'It was narrated that Aishah said:\n&ldquo;The Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) came in one day looking happy, and said: O Aishah, did you not see that Mujazziz Al-Mudliji entered upon me and saw Usamah and Zaid. There was a blanket over them and their faces were covered but their feet were exposed, and he said: These feet belong to one another.&rdquo;',
