      'It was narrated that Abu Uthman Nahdi said:\n&ldquo;I heard Sad and Abu Bakrah both say that they heard directly from Muhammad (ﷺ) saying it and memorized: Whoever claims to belong to someone other than his father knowing the he is not his father, Paradise will be forbidden to him.&rdquo;',
