      'It was narrated from Aishah that the freed slave of the Prophet (ﷺ) fell from a palm tree and died. He left behind wealth but he had no child or close relative. The Prophet (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;Give his legacy to a man from his village.&rdquo;',
