      'It was narrated from Wathilah bin Asqa that the Prophet (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;A woman may get three types of inheritance: From her freed slave woman, a foundling whom she raised, and her child concerning whom she swore in Lian that he was legitimate.&rdquo;',
