      'Abdullah bin Amr said:\n&ldquo;I heard the Prophet (ﷺ) say: There is no band of warriors that fights in the cause of Allah and acquires war spoils, but they have been given two thirds of their reward, but if they do not get any spoils of war, then they will have their reward in full (in the Hereafter).&rdquo;',
