      'It was narrated from Abu Hurairah that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) said:\n&ldquo;The pilgrims performing Hajj and Umrah are a delegation to Allah. If they call upon Him, He will answer them; and if they ask for His forgiveness, He will forgive them.&rdquo;',
