      'It was narrated from Ibn Umar that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) came and performed Tawaf around the House seven times, then he prayed two Rakahs. Waki said:\n&ldquo;Meaning, at the Maqam,* then he went out to Safa.&rdquo;',
